The global Field Service Management (FSM) market is expected to witness significant growth by the year 2031, with a strong CAGR. The market is segmented by components, deployment types, organization sizes, end-users, and geography. The key components in the market include software and services. Deployment types are categorized into cloud-based and on-premises solutions. Organizations can choose FSM solutions based on their size, such as Small and Medium-Sized Enterprises (SMEs) or large enterprises. Various industries drive the demand for FSM, including manufacturing, healthcare, telecom, construction, energy and utilities, among others. Geographically, the market is spread across regions like North America, Europe, Asia-Pacific, South America, and the Middle East and Africa.

